Adam Crapser, 39, of Salem, Oregon, was issued with deportation papers by the Department of Homeland Security in January and a hearing hearing is set for April 2 .
The father-of-three was adopted from South Korea as a toddler around the age of three .
His first set of adoptive parents abandoned him and the second set turned out to be abusive by another adoptive family .
Crapser is now facing deportation because his U.S. citizenship was never registered .